data.description: Single Story with Mature Landscape and Beautiful Shade Tree in Sidewalked Rosemary Ridge! Fresh paint and New Carpet throughout! The stone entry welcomes you into the expansive hall with art niche. This flex plan allows the french door study to serve as a perfect retreat for remote work or a second living room. The entertainer's kitchen has bar seating, service bar, electric range, built in microwave, large pantry and sunny morning room. The high ceiling living room has decorative ledge and wood flooring. All secondary beds are large with ample closet space and direct access to the full bath with shower tub combo and custom vanity. The Primary suite has vaulted ceiling, large walk in closet, en suite bath with dual sink vanity, large soaking tub, linen closet and separate shower with rain head. Backyard has 13 x 7 covered patio and huge private yard. Beautiful greenbelt with walking trails nearby. HVAC 2022. Fence 2023. Roof 2017.
